message.body: I was thinking we could meet at your apt tomorrow because the lobster roll place is east of new haven. What time is good for you?
Anytime, I'm free all day! Any chance i could interest you in bowling as well? :-D If not, just lobster is fine too!
Ha ha. No worries, it'll be fun! Let me know :-)
Is 12:30 ok? We can pick you up. And we can decide tomorrow when to go bowling. I think the place down the street from me is like 15 after 5pm for 2
How about I pick you up at 7 for bowling? They said it's six bucks a game tonight
